Annual Vienna Economic Forum Summits and “Vienna Economic Forum Talks” (last 5 years): 
In 2017: 14th Vienna Economic Forum – Vienna Future Dialogue 2017; Vienna Economic Talks - Belgrade Meeting 2017 
In 2016: 13th Vienna Economic Forum – Vienna Future Dialogue 2016; 
In 2015: 12th Vienna Economic Forum - Vienna Dialogue 2015 - Investments as a motor for Competitiveness and Growth; 
“Vienna Economic Forum Talks” in Tirana with Prime Ministers of Albania, Bosnia Herzegovina, Montenegro, Serbia, Kosovo Territory, FYROM; 
In 2014: 11th Vienna Economic Forum - Vienna Summit 2014 - Visions and Responsibilities in a Changing Time;  
“Vienna Economic Forum Talks” in Istanbul;  
EU - Moldova International Investors' Conference; 
In 2013: 10th Jubilee Vienna Economic Forum - „Visions and Visionaries. The Economy is the Motor"; 
“Vienna Economic Forum Talks” in Zagreb (entry of Croatia in EU); 
In 2012: 9th Vienna Economic Forum - “Quo vadis, Europe? Regional Cooperation for European Integration”.
